{"tid":385493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"快來拍扁IT狗吧!!!!!","createTime":"2017-09-03T09:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T05:56:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7ba0ad4dad9f709267e304ccf6fd3190b100ee","tid":385493,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:27:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://mt.m-t.hk/31production.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmt.m-t.hk%2F31production.html&d=bPK0oh70e0%2B6TKpohi9AyWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7a7115bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://mt.m-t.hk/31production.html</a><br />\n打不死IT狗<br />\n<br />\n組件一共10件，必須順序黏貼標記處，才可以製作出打不死IT狗。<br />\n<br />\n步驟一　黏貼1至5〔製作影片〕<br />\n步驟二　黏貼6至9〔製作影片〕<br />\n步驟三　黏貼10至12〔製作影片〕<br />\n步驟四　黏貼13至14〔製作影片〕<br />\n<br />\n快來拍扁IT狗吧<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o6Zt9q1j7EZHDmJDW/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o6Zt9q1j7EZHDmJDW%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3b2e1816&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9da8ca61dd6129228b5fa7b5c5843434dd95b571","tid":385493,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"IT雖受到社會各階層的歡迎，但以IT為生的職業員工卻屬於「賤民」，地位在平民之下。雖然有些當紅的IT人，能夠擠身豪們，成為達官貴人的座上客，然而在世人的眼中，他們的人格仍然是低下的，因為IT是供人娛樂的「玩意兒」，IT人就是為人取樂的。 <br />\n<br />\n看不起IT人並不僅僅是官宦階層，民間的百姓也同樣視IT為最下賤的職業。普通人家如有人去做「IT」，都會被認為是有辱祖宗，是不肖子孫。凡做「IT」的人要被開除族籍，名字不能上族譜，死後不能葬入宗族墳地。因此，很多人從IT之後，隱姓埋名，幾十年不與家族來往，以免玷辱祖宗。"},{"pid":"fceb469f9cd4616b7d7e31d5e78ca0311c7f0329","tid":385493,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"千呼萬喚的「超級無敵IT狗」終於回來了！珍妮遇上大廈停電要爬樓梯；洗澡時又突然沒有水供應。究竟停電和停水之間有什麼關係？一向傻氣十足的IT狗在協助珍妮解決沒有水洗澡的煩惱時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，又會鬧出什麼笑話？"},{"pid":"c540ab3fcbc66d7e15e41460eb50c79755f9e0ab","tid":385493,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://mt.m-t.hk/1004magazine.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmt.m-t.hk%2F1004magazine.asp&d=bPK0oh70e0%2B6TKpohi9AyWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=60b537f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://mt.m-t.hk/1004magazine.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n如何使用插頭、萬能蘇及拖板才是最安全的？通過珍妮和IT狗日常生活的有趣小故事，我們會為大家逐一解答疑問。[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如何抽插珍妮才是最安全的..... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5d1f94f808ecc133da25118689f0f080f2e93b","tid":385493,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"原來IT狗有名, 叫阿寶<br />\n<br />\n人地有女嫁<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/14/005233_8f88c6ad84e4cbae7d450ed0c84f0973.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F14%2F005233_8f88c6ad84e4cbae7d450ed0c84f0973.jpg&h=c9a6cf34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64f497a52d1965ba2b620f96a17b4925a5e6a732","tid":385493,"uid":126902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T09:33:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來IT狗有名, 叫阿寶<br />\n<br />\n人地有女嫁&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/14/005233_8f88c6ad84e4cbae7d450ed0c84f0973.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F14%2F005233_8f88c6ad84e4cbae7d450ed0c84f0973.jpg%22&d=bPK0oh70e0%2B6TKpohi9AyWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=23e4b8bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-